  you can send an invitation by email to whomever you'd like to invite. You and your fellow attendees can vote on dates, times, and locations that work for you.
  <br>
  <center><%= link_to "Get Started", events_path, class:"button get-started", id: "get_started" %></center>
<% end %>

</div>

